= Usage

You just do
  require 'rubyflight'
Everything is under the RubyFlight module.

= Testing & Example

There's a test.rb file which is a tinty client application to FS using
RubyFlight. You can use this as an example. To run this, just do
  ruby test.rb
with FS open, and you'll get a periodical reading of various FS variables.
